channel.title: PI - FridderScape - Highscore board/Korasi/Spawning server
channel.description:
[size=28pt]FridderScape[/size]
I'm releasing this. I have like 5 versions of this server :P. This is like v3 or 4... The base is PI (Project Insanity). Nothing 'extra special' about the server. I've had at the most 20 online. When you download this, make sure to make it so the items that are for donators aren't spawnable. I can post the code if somebody requests it... Good luck with this server.
[b][u]Downloads:[/u][/b] Server: http://www.mediafire.com/?4lniyrrydmsb6fh Client: http://www.mediafire.com/?dzo9xwx18lm684f
[b][u]Features:[/u][/b] Fun PK. Pk point system. Korasi Slayer helmets PvP Armors #1 Pker online scoreboard No anti-leech. Etc...
Pictures:
